title: Did the dolphins and pelicans return to the Italian waterways in mid-COVID-19 lock?
subtitle: Some wildlife scenes were enthusiastically shared through social media as a note of the sunny news in the dark reality of the Corona virus epidemic.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: In the midst of a state-wide insurance operation COVID-19, Italians reported the vision of wildlife such as pelicans and dolphins "return" to newly quiet waterways, ports and channels.
